<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177301>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Palpus of the male, lateral view. (a) Lispe latana; (b) L. levis; (c) L. lisarba; (d) L. serotina; (e) L. setuligera; (f) L. tentaculata; (g) L. vilis. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177301/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177303>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Fore tarsi of the male. (a) Lispe latana; (b) L. levis; (c) L. serotina; (d) L. setuligera; (e) L. tentaculata; (f) L. vilis. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177303/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177297>
    dc:description "Figure 1. (a) Lispe setuligera. Mid tibia, lateral view; (b) L. serotina. Mid tibia, dorsal view; (c) L. setuligera. Hind femur, posterior view; (d) L. vilis. Hind femur, posterior view; (e) L. tentaculata. Fore metatarsus, lateral view; (f) L. vilis. Fore metatarsus, lateral view; (g) L. vilis. Wing, lateral view; (h) L. rufitibialis. Wing, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177297/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5177299>
    dc:description "Figure 2. (a) Lispe latana. Dorsocentral, presutural setae, lateral view; (b) L. levis. Dorsocentral, presutural setae, lateral view; (c) L. serotina. Dorsocentral, postsutural setae, lateral view; (d) L. levis. Dorsocentral, postsutural setae, lateral view; (e) L. levis. Head, frontal view; (f) L. lisarba. Head, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5177299/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

